text: Henrique Costa da Silva (born ) is a Brazilian-born Armenian futsal player who plays as a winger for FC Kingersheim after a short stint at Portimonense. Henrique Costa became an international for the Armenia national futsal team in 2019. ==References== ==External links== *The Final Ball profile Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian men's futsal players Category:Armenian men's futsal players
